 150:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) Different sequential I2C interfaces are listed below:
 151:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) Sequential transmit in master I2C mode an amount of data in non-blocking mode using
 152:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****             HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_IT() or using HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_DMA()
 153:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+++) At transmission end of current frame transfer, HAL_I2C_MasterTxCpltCallback() is execut
