1053:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****        (++) Blocking mode : The communication is performed in the polling mode.
1054:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****             The status of all data processing is returned by the same function
1055:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****             after finishing transfer.
